title: 11/17/21 DPS Hour 1 Dan Orlovsky

description:
Dan Orlovsky tells Dan that Tom Brady is hard to come up with new compliments for because he has been so good for so long. Dan says that Patrick Mahomes is still good but other QB's have played better.
